name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
Netizen contribution
On June 13, an old farmer in Fujian was fined 100,000 yuan for selling vegetables for a profit of 14 yuan, which was reported by many media and attracted attention.
It is reported that an old farmer in Fujian sold vegetables of substandard quality in 2019 and was investigated by the local Municipal Supervision Bureau in 2021. On April 22, 2022, the Municipal Supervision Bureau made a decision to fine the old farmer 50,000 yuan, and later added another 50,000 yuan, totaling 100,000 yuan. Because the old man was unable to pay the fine, the Municipal Supervision Bureau applied to the Minhou Court for compulsory execution against the old man. However, the Minhou Court believed that the Municipal Supervision Bureau's decision to fine the old man was too heavy and the procedure was illegal, so it was not enforced.

On June 13, the police of Yanta Police Station of Zengcheng District Branch of Guangzhou Public Security Bureau responded to the man's participation in setting up a sneak photography website abroad.
According to the investigation, Guangzhou man Tang Mouran participated in setting up a sneak photography website abroad and made profits from it. His place of origin is Zengcheng, Guangzhou. He has not entered the country yet. The community police have visited his residence, but no one is at home. The police have communicated with the property management to keep an eye on Tang Mouran.
